/// Fixture gr-01: `sub … at auto` + a member-level `relate { }` block
/// (geometric-relations v0_6, PRD §1/§3 G3/§9 task δ; design §1/§4/§5).
///
/// Signal: `tree-sitter parse --quiet gr-01-at-auto-relate.ri` exits 0 once the
/// δ grammar steps land. Needs `at auto` (step-4) + member-level `relate { }`
/// (step-6). ERRORs on the base grammar (`relate`/`at auto` not yet accepted).
structure Assembly {
    sub plate : Plate
    sub bolt : Bolt at auto
    relate {
        concentric(bolt.shank.axis, plate.hole.axis)
        flush(bolt.head.seat, plate.top.plane)
    }
}
